This page provides a list of the FHIR artifacts defined as part of this implementation guide.


Structures: Resource Profiles {% capture grouping_desc %}These define constraints on FHIR resources for systems conforming to this implementation guide.{% endcapture %}
    {{ grouping_desc | markdownify}}





               Allergy Intolerance Profile for Immunization Decision Support

            {% capture desc %}Profile for allergy intolerances relevant to immunization. The code (allergen/substance) may use SNOMED CT or ICD-10-CM. Reaction substances may use CVX, MVX, SNOMED CT, or RxNorm.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Condition Profile with Vaccine Condition Codes

            {% capture desc %}Profile for conditions where the code must be from the Vaccine Condition Codes value set. Accepts SNOMED CT and ICD-10-CM coded conditions.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Dose of a Vaccine

            {% capture desc %}Detailed information about each vaccination dose.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Immunization Procedures Profile

            {% capture desc %}Profile for medical procedures related to immunization based on SNOMED CT or CPT codes.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Medication Administration Profile with Vaccine Codes

            {% capture desc %}Profile for medication administrations with vaccine codes from CVX or MVX.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Medication Dispense Profile with Vaccine Codes

            {% capture desc %}Profile for medication dispenses with vaccine codes from CVX or MVX.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Medication Request Profile with Vaccine Codes

            {% capture desc %}Profile for medication requests with vaccine codes from CVX or MVX.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Medication Statement Profile with Vaccine Codes

            {% capture desc %}Profile for medication statements with vaccine codes from CVX or MVX.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Observation Profile for Immunization Decision Support

            {% capture desc %}Profile for Observation resources carrying lab evidence of immunity or other findings relevant to immunization decisions. Codes may be from SNOMED CT, ICD-10-CM, or LOINC.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Vaccination Patient

            {% capture desc %}A profile that extends the base FHIR Patient resource to include detailed vaccination-related information.{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}




               Vaccine

            {% capture desc %}Simple vaccine to easily obtain needed information for forecasting{% endcapture %}
{{ desc | markdownify}}





